title: President's Day, Favorite Moments, Parents, Dating and more.

description:
Happy President's Day y'all.  What's more appropriate for your story a thick book or thin book?  There are certain things that are said that show us that we are becoming our parents.  Is dating worth it?  How would you react if you suspected you man of cheating.  Can a man really out argue a female or nah?  The fellas tell us the things that they say to their neighbors under their breath.  That knot on your head does not look like you fell.  Today in Closing Remarks, The CEO talks about the importance of resiliency and more.
